CM-LRS — Companion code, prompts, rubrics, demonstration tasks, and scoring data
=================================================================================

This repository is the public companion release for the paper:

  Ahuja, P. (2026). Capital Markets LLM Reliability Score (CM-LRS):
  From Plausible to Bankable.

